com.chdryra.android.reviewer

Interface Review

  • All Superinterfaces:
    RDId.RDIdAble
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ReviewNode, ReviewNodeExpandable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ReviewComponent, ReviewEditable, ReviewNodeAlone, ReviewNull, ReviewTree, ReviewTreeEditable, ReviewUser, ReviewUserEditable

    public interface Review
extends RDId.RDIdAble
    The fundamental interface for all review classes. All reviews are primarily data holders that are expected to have 3 items of core data:
    • A unique identifier
    • A subject
    • A rating
    In addition, reviews may have some optional data:
    • Comments
    • Images
    • Locations
    • Facts
    • URLs
    Reviews can be nodes in a review tree with children sub-reviews and/or be a sub-review of a parent review. They can be represented as a ReviewNode with zero or more children and/or a parent if necessary. Reviews may or may not be published (have non-null @see Author and Publish Date)
    See Also:
    ReviewNode, ReviewEditable, ReviewUser
